# 下载

1. 下载：[homebrew install](https://www.rabbitmq.com/install-homebrew.html)
```
~ » brew install rabbitmq
....
```

2. 把rabbitmq命令加入环境变量中

```
echo 'export PATH="/usr/local/Cellar/rabbitmq/3.7.15/sbin:$PATH"' >> ~/.zshrc
```

# 运行

1. 启动服务
```
~ » rabbitmq-server -detached
Warning: PID file not written; -detached was passed.
```
